high_descs: turn around and walk past the chairs on your right, then walk forwards to the TV stand on your left
grab a credit card off of the TV stand there
turn right and walk forwards a few steps, then take a right and walk to the left side of the couch at the end of the room, and turn right to face it
place the credit card down on top of the couch there
turn right and walk to the TV stand again at the end of the room on the left
grab another credit card off of the TV stand there
turn right and walk forwards a few steps, then take a right and walk to the left side of the couch at the end of the room, and turn right to face it
place the credit card down on top of the couch there

high_descs: Turn left then head to the tv stand
Pick up the credit card in front of the tv
Turn right then head to the end of the long sofa on the left
Put the credit card on the sofa
Turn right then head back to the tv stand
Pick up the credit card in front of the tv
Turn right then head to the end of the sofa on the left
Put the credit card on top of the other on the sofa

high_descs: Turn around, move to the wall, turn right, move to the TV, turn left to face the TV.
Pick up the credit card at that back of the TV stand.
Turn right, move to the wall, turn right, move to the wall, turn right to face the left side of the couch.
Put the credit card under the blue pillow on the couch.
Turn right, move back to the TV across the room on the left.
Pick up the credit card on the TV stand.
Turn right, move to the wall, turn right, move to the wall, turn right to face the left side of the couch.
Put the credit card on the couch, left of the other credit card.
